{"tid":1346472,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"請開始籌組臨時立法會","createTime":"2019-07-22T04:14:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-22T12:05:31.000Z","uid":14256,"like":85,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"1eb9af43e62160b370f2951da591ec9b153d0b50","tid":1346472,"uid":14256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T04:14:48.000Z","msg":"到左哩個時候，到左警黑建制行埋一齊既地步，個議會一早失左效。<br />\n<br />\n請大家發揮力量，準備籌組臨時立法會。<br />\n我地絕對歡迎建制派一齊參選。"},{"pid":"16e07a63fe67b36600815e1e682ab6f364bca503","tid":1346472,"uid":14256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T04:30:43.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"bea60c0da1104c3e30d3fd2a36b0fc0641736ba6","tid":1346472,"uid":235025,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T04:31:58.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"70b2f330e1bd9e60f9568a97f4fa359563bccfc2","tid":1346472,"uid":270525,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T04:32:02.000Z","msg":"係臨時國會，唔好再用立法會個名，臭曬"},{"pid":"3397c5e2292a4993a24fefb530dfbed4633e8516","tid":1346472,"uid":103127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T04:33:08.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e2c75f8dee53552e9e4d643a4c7d5b915b40ddff","tid":1346472,"uid":23993,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T04:33:14.000Z","msg":"憲法先呀<br />\n憲法先呀<br />\n憲法先呀<br />\n搵law友開始幫手寫啦"},{"pid":"7b590681706e1462162c0e2d823ce798e598b1f9","tid":1346472,"uid":14256,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"70b2f330e1bd9e60f9568a97f4fa359563bccfc2","tid":1346472,"uid":270525,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T04:32:02.000Z","msg":"係臨時國會，唔好再用立法會個名，臭曬"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T04:34:30.000Z","msg":"名稱唔係重點，用途先係<br />\n<br />\n用立法會個名可以暫時增加認受性，無咁易俾人話獨立住，易d入屋，可以爭取最多人討論<br />\n到真係成功再用國會一詞都唔遲"},{"pid":"b2120bd8308df859f386a7e7fc80c96c27bd312c","tid":1346472,"uid":271857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T04:34:40.000Z","msg":"